><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通餐廳，高檔茶記</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n檸茶點整<br />\n聽講除咗茶仲有另外一啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍定熱先<br />\n其實好唔好飲主要係睇紅茶煲得靚唔靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍<br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇熱奶茶 係咪落花奶 比例幾比幾"},{"pid":"7c2c0ffca40f8f32444adc6d0b3bd393c41bd97e","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n檸茶點整<br />\n聽講除咗茶仲有另外一啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍定熱先<br />\n其實好唔好飲主要係睇紅茶煲得靚唔靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍<br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇熱奶茶 係咪落花奶 比例幾比幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n半杯紅茶（真係茶，無溝女，勁濃）<br />\n淨返都係花奶"},{"pid":"240fb6e5ea2c7e6aaddcd51e2e265f74e4a02774","tid":54244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍定熱先<br />\n其實好唔好飲主要係睇紅茶煲得靚唔靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍<br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇熱奶茶 係咪落花奶 比例幾比幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n半杯紅茶（真係茶，無溝女，勁濃）<br />\n淨返都係花奶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n50 50 㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前整係70茶 30花奶"},{"pid":"a30947a9677929b0bbf7f1b2b516985e2d0658d3","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n檸茶點整<br />\n聽講除咗茶仲有另外一啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍定熱先<br />\n其實好唔好飲主要係睇紅茶煲得靚唔靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍<br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇熱奶茶 係咪落花奶 比例幾比幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍檸茶其實都係熱檸茶，熱個陣加糖，搞溶再攤到室溫，然後放雪櫃，通常整定幾卓"},{"pid":"53a84eaee1e5d0934c1afad8c088ebca4bcfa2d3","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍<br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇熱奶茶 係咪落花奶 比例幾比幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n半杯紅茶（真係茶，無溝女，勁濃）<br />\n淨返都係花奶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n50 50 㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前整係70茶 30花奶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我個到煲到d紅茶好濃，所以5050 色水最靚同好飲d"},{"pid":"17583298ed67da032b9049d7524a094abb71a9dc","tid":54244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"自學定係有師傅教<br />\n定係老細求其教你鳩整"},{"pid":"c1ed108caa1ae19077108f5de0a4209766393237","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自學定係有師傅教<br />\n定係老細求其教你鳩整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水吧佬教，佢淨係做早午市，下午茶同夜晚我整"},{"pid":"5d35280b9254a672445b3936f4d52abee7aa9272","tid":54244,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍定熱先<br />\n其實好唔好飲主要係睇紅茶煲得靚唔靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍<br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇熱奶茶 係咪落花奶 比例幾比幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍檸茶其實都係熱檸茶，熱個陣加糖，搞溶再攤到室溫，然後放雪櫃，通常整定幾卓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n杯茶澀撚到晒咁"},{"pid":"072ae2bab4ac36d36e581c593beed45281b38fae","tid":54244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自學定係有師傅教<br />\n定係老細求其教你鳩整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水吧佬教，佢淨係做早午市，下午茶同夜晚我整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我以前係老細教我鳩整<br />\n我都唔知佢係咪熟手<br />\n所以我亦唔知我係咪做得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390893077d824dedb722d3abca4b5c3a1a49b0bd","tid":54244,"uid":65185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"水吧係咪做極都係萬幾蚊？<br />\n過2萬都好少？"},{"pid":"34938189381b8aaa251baf5644b500df760601ac","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍<br />\n<br />\nbtw有冇熱奶茶 係咪落花奶 比例幾比幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凍檸茶其實都係熱檸茶，熱個陣加糖，搞溶再攤到室溫，然後放雪櫃，通常整定幾卓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n杯茶澀撚到晒咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過仲有另一種整法，我覺得呢隻好飲d同大路d所以我整親都係呢隻：<br />\n濃紅茶 1/3卓，再加糖水"},{"pid":"8ce2d924fdde0e3c57d89b2e3a08259e2173de49","tid":54244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水吧係咪做極都係萬幾蚊？<br />\n過2萬都好少？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過老細請人whatsapp group<br />\n最多17000 18000<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e031f69a63bf82c5449705febe37a81c4e52690","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水吧係咪做極都係萬幾蚊？<br />\n過2萬都好少？</blockquote><br />\n唔知，我個陣做waiter 但夜晚我變做水吧個位咁解"},{"pid":"28a48e029a2597ea74697a29f3e251e4dcaa0414","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自學定係有師傅教<br />\n定係老細求其教你鳩整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水吧佬教，佢淨係做早午市，下午茶同夜晚我整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我以前係老細教我鳩整<br />\n我都唔知佢係咪熟手<br />\n所以我亦唔知我係咪做得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好多時都係隨心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係忙個陣<br />\n有陣時多有陣時少 都係大約咁樣<br />\n連「不」花奶個個殼都唔用，直接拎起成罐倒落去"},{"pid":"3a19d38bd2f45e78fa4fcec7c5468d9f8dc231e1","tid":54244,"uid":7613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"奶茶點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703afd51729386f47d0c4b3572af7f43e161dfe3","tid":54244,"uid":7613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶茶點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話邊隻紅茶"},{"pid":"427cf45492d46aa3b8bf861516dda8e8583190f3","tid":54244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水吧佬教，佢淨係做早午市，下午茶同夜晚我整</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我以前係老細教我鳩整<br />\n我都唔知佢係咪熟手<br />\n所以我亦唔知我係咪做得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好多時都係隨心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係忙個陣<br />\n有陣時多有陣時少 都係大約咁樣<br />\n連「不」花奶個個殼都唔用，直接拎起成罐倒落去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係本來就直接倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769bcdfcba624d2dd33f419fabce3b1c5dc7cbe8","tid":54244,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"用咩牌子既茶葉整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2ec437983a6fd6b971bbdb003d2a8508cbd76d","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奶茶點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話邊隻紅茶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水吧有煲茶機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用茶葉煲的<br />\n屋企整就唔知 最好濃少少<br />\n加完花奶之後茶味都係到"},{"pid":"c41cba2cfc18bc708d242e0f5143336e2c37c2b7","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用咩牌子既茶葉整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真係無留意過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個袋透明無字"},{"pid":"cb6f686bfafbf8110d1b2441b598d5a373351651","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:46:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奶茶點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n濃紅茶+花奶=奶茶"},{"pid":"81b9e6e3b20cf4e9a8cd76e5a295eb3132c5d2d0","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我以前係老細教我鳩整<br />\n我都唔知佢係咪熟手<br />\n所以我亦唔知我係咪做得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好多時都係隨心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係忙個陣<br />\n有陣時多有陣時少 都係大約咁樣<br />\n連「不」花奶個個殼都唔用，直接拎起成罐倒落去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係本來就直接倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估唔到侵侵都做過水吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0796247617d1935070866b9c9b64b61ca20135f7","tid":54244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好多時都係隨心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係忙個陣<br />\n有陣時多有陣時少 都係大約咁樣<br />\n連「不」花奶個個殼都唔用，直接拎起成罐倒落去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係本來就直接倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估唔到侵侵都做過水吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又係水吧兼任樓面"},{"pid":"7a46efcf67afee15dfc8c15890e6e2d2eae6e866","tid":54244,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:30:39.000Z","msg":"檸水係咪水喉水沖？<br />\n果 d 絲襪奶茶，搵茶又係咩料？"},{"pid":"33c661cdc880ca237948ebb9aff04151401fe395","tid":54244,"uid":69738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"有無試過加料落啲野飲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05635c3d6a5e8fec794534a9fc3785bc537dc822","tid":54244,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>檸水係咪水喉水沖？<br />\n果 d 絲襪奶茶，搵茶又係咩料？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱既通常唔會 但凍嘅少甜同走甜都係落生水<br />\n利申 樓面 成日望住個水吧佬咁沖"},{"pid":"21c570aaf6b281ed4762bfdbbc9654ce7556b7c1","tid":54244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>檸水係咪水喉水沖？<br />\n果 d 絲襪奶茶，搵茶又係咩料？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱既通常唔會 但凍嘅少甜同走甜都係落生水<br />\n利申 樓面 成日望住個水吧佬咁沖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢直接係水喉出水？<br />\n<br />\n我之前係喺熱水爐出水<br />\n如果知道會忙嘅話會煲定一壺放喺煲茶度保溫<br />\n我從來唔用生水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該好少會用生水掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49201c4c095233f014b34a4a4bdfc84e5b374d2","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>檸水係咪水喉水沖？<br />\n果 d 絲襪奶茶，搵茶又係咩料？</blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n熱檸水係檸檬＋滾水<br />\n凍檸水就係檸檬加糖水加冰"},{"pid":"045e00195f74e2e82b65b42fb975a0f72733fb20","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>檸水係咪水喉水沖？<br />\n果 d 絲襪奶茶，搵茶又係咩料？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱既通常唔會 但凍嘅少甜同走甜都係落生水<br />\n利申 樓面 成日望住個水吧佬咁沖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢直接係水喉出水？<br />\n<br />\n我之前係喺熱水爐出水<br />\n如果知道會忙嘅話會煲定一壺放喺煲茶度保溫<br />\n我從來唔用生水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該好少會用生水掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係架，少甜係會落生水架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090d6a105731d23a8f97b498b96cd110d78aad22","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無試過加料落啲野飲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我份人比較乾淨<br />\n一污染就倒，唔要，重整新杯"},{"pid":"288df9caaa02693ed9ae3b3d2e36b49e7f7d7340","tid":54244,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱既通常唔會 但凍嘅少甜同走甜都係落生水<br />\n利申 樓面 成日望住個水吧佬咁沖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢直接係水喉出水？<br />\n<br />\n我之前係喺熱水爐出水<br />\n如果知道會忙嘅話會煲定一壺放喺煲茶度保溫<br />\n我從來唔用生水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該好少會用生水掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係架，少甜係會落生水架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11e0076f6737f6279d6f8923ebf7e9f5f5c74df","tid":54244,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"想問下邊樣野飲成本最貴？"},{"pid":"7768225bd417247e69075fa03e0680f6848a3073","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱既通常唔會 但凍嘅少甜同走甜都係落生水<br />\n利申 樓面 成日望住個水吧佬咁沖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢直接係水喉出水？<br />\n<br />\n我之前係喺熱水爐出水<br />\n如果知道會忙嘅話會煲定一壺放喺煲茶度保溫<br />\n我從來唔用生水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該好少會用生水掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係架，少甜係會落生水架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n滾水熱得濟，加完糖水都cooldown唔到幾多<br />\n落冰D冰會溶<br />\n水吧又唔會特登裝幾卓水黎攤凍<br />\n一黎要好多時間攤凍，二黎無位，會阻住做野<br />\n三黎用攤水既水係唔夠用，所以廢事煩落生水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以少甜既檸水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31773d3d9730660e325b454cace0753bb4a436dc","tid":54244,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:46:28.000Z","msg":"凍飲少甜點解咁難飲？"},{"pid":"b2c2b30b6307432eef5160f765f426b794fc96ac","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下邊樣野飲成本最貴？</blockquote><br />\n唔計特飲個堆<br />\n正路都係奶茶架啦<br />\n靚茶葉，又要煲，擺左某段時間又要再煲過新既，唔要舊茶等等...<br />\n同埋花奶用得好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57ba89b0580b209634828497025fc3677bd7672","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>凍飲少甜點解咁難飲？</blockquote><br />\n咩凍飲先<br />\n茶類？如果少甜難飲既話應該係茶底唔好<br />\n我個間真係好注重個茶底既<br />\n水吧佬要每朝6點返到黎煲定茶，靚茶<br />\n就算加完其他野，奶茶同檸茶都飲得出茶味<br />\n而家市面上面好多都係茶底垃圾，飲糖水咁"},{"pid":"680e638033bce173869f93d35a06633cc16bfc27","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好多時都係隨心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係忙個陣<br />\n有陣時多有陣時少 都係大約咁樣<br />\n連「不」花奶個個殼都唔用，直接拎起成罐倒落去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係本來就直接倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n估唔到侵侵都做過水吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又係水吧兼任樓面</blockquote><br />\n唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cf0fe6e8b0d860c1f57cff2f53271e55f4a0d6","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"各位最好其實都係少D飲凍飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2f38779b4125eec2a9ab6f98ea058fe0672618","tid":54244,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"笑撚左 自稱高檔<br />\n但冷0茶唔係茶同糖水分開上<br />\n你知唔知咩叫高檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651aebb07b0749f424fd670d84b705f40be58d34","tid":54244,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑撚左 自稱高檔<br />\n但冷0茶唔係茶同糖水分開上<br />\n你知唔知咩叫高檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高檔茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n茶記呀"},{"pid":"d61e3ebb900cee3e8bb6dd69e6ab3d12898e2f04","tid":54244,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78adabd506fc5bafc49f4b59778b020a4d7e5a18","tid":54244,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>笑撚左 自稱高檔<br />\n但冷0茶唔係茶同糖水分開上<br />\n你知唔知咩叫高檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高檔茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n茶記呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話撚左你唔識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有茶記係分開上架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdb5926cedcdbe09b476746875850a06548aa8d","tid":54244,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"高檔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}